data.description: This is a gorgeous 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath GHO home on a half-acre in the beautiful, gated community of Stoney Brook Farm! High grand ceilings, impact windows, custom built-ins throughout, marble-looking tile, and water softener. Library with rolling ladder, wine bar, large 3-car garage with work benches, EV charging station, in-ceiling surround sound, Bahamian shutters, and so much more!
